name: deposit your adoration four
description: writhe in the tepid waters of your blue light toilet until your destroyed hole opens. until two decades of senseless obligation saturate the pictures of people you'll never talk to again. with half digested arby's. and six tums that did nothing to pacify your eternal indigestion. blast every morsel of your large intestine for an eternity until you get the momentary satisfaction you seek. until the coils overflow. then you'll be happy. then you can tell someone you did something.
